Ayo.

00:01:01.480 --> 00:01:02.647
Apa yang kamu tunggu?

00:01:02.932 --> 00:01:04.557
Saya..
- Ya?

00:01:04.906 --> 00:01:06.113
Saya..

00:01:10.020 --> 00:01:12.020
Ya Tuhan!  Dia pingsan.

00:01:13.313 --> 00:01:15.939
Preesha!  Air!

